title: T-Mobile OnePlus 9 and OnePlus 9 Pro finally get the Android 12 update with OxygenOS 12
content:
The unlocked OnePlus 9 and 9 Pro received the stable Android 12 update with OxygenOS 12 back in December 2021. Three months later, T-Mobile is finally rolling out the latest software to the OnePlus 9 series in the US. The update comes with a software version LE2117_11.C.16 (for 9) / LE2127_11.C.16 (for 9 Pro), and

description: The OnePlus 9 and 9 Pro on T-Mobile are receiving their respective stable OxygenOS 12 updates based on Android 12. Read on to know more!
